headline: Lennar Announces Final Exchange Ratio of 4.1367 in Exchange Offer
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B) ("Lennar") announced today a final exchange ratio of 4.1367 (the "Final Exchange Ratio") for its previously announced offer to exchange up to 33,298,764 shares of Millrose Properties, Inc. (NYSE: MRP) ("Millrose") Class A stock it owns (approximately 20% total outstanding Millrose stock) for outstanding shares of Lennar Class A common stock (the "Exchange Offer").
